description: Ask listing agent about seller concessions for an interest rate-buy down!! Welcome to highly sought over East 2nd street location in Red Hot Southie! Prime turn-key opportunity to own this fully renovated 1 bed 1 bath second-floor unit! You're welcomed in by an open concept layout with a massive fully renovated kitchen leading to an open living room. This unit features one of the larger bedrooms you'll find in Southie, complete with a washer and dryer hookups, and a walk-in closet. This unit features a large storage closet in the basement. Nothing to do, but to move in and start building immediate equity in this top of the line unit! Welcome to Southie!
